726522f-a.title: Queens: Eldert Street - Wyckoff Avenue
726522f-a.text:
Eldert Street (left), south fromm Wyckoff Ave. to Long Island
Railroad rioht of wav, in a set of two views. No.1 shows the
S.W. and No. 2 the S.E. corners. View No. 1 is in Brooklyn and
View No. 2 shows the dividing line which is the center of the Street;
and a line of garages on the Queens County side.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

728048f-a.text:

726521f-a.title: Queens: Eldert Street - Wyckoff Avenue
726521f-a.text:
Eldert Street, south from Wyckoff Ave. The center of this street
is the dividing line between Kings and Queens Counties. The last named
is on the east side of the Street.
October 1928.
